### Create an event (Azure Functions local)
POST http://localhost:7071/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Indie Rock Concert",
  "venue": "Town Hall",
  "ticketPrice": { "amount": 2500, "currency": "USD" },
  "totalCapacity": 200,
  "date": "2026-06-01T19:00:00Z"
}

### Example using `curl`
# curl -X POST http://localhost:7071/api/events \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"name":"Indie Rock Concert","venue":"Town Hall","ticketPrice":{"amount":2500,"currency":"USD"},"totalCapacity":200,"date":"2026-06-01T19:00:00Z", "reservationExpirationInSeconds": "60"}'
